    <item>
      <title>HTB Archetype</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/blog/htb_archetype/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 May 2026 14:40:33 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/blog/htb_archetype/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;preface&#34; class=&#34;mt-8 mb-3 text-xl sm:text-2xl text-white&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;relative inline-block&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      Preface&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;span&#xD;&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute left-0 -bottom-1 h-px w-0 bg-indigo-400&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I approached this box as a boot to root style CTF.&#xA;In this write up I step through my methodology and thought process behind it.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;active-reconnaissance&#34; class=&#34;mt-8 mb-3 text-xl sm:text-2xl text-white&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;relative inline-block&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      Active reconnaissance&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;span&#xD;&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute left-0 -bottom-1 h-px w-0 bg-indigo-400&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;After connecting to the VPN and waiting for the box server to start responding to my pings, it&amp;rsquo;s ready for some enumeration.&#xA;To start off, a fast Nmap &lt;em&gt;SYN&lt;/em&gt; scan across the whole port range.&#xA;&lt;em&gt;arch is set as hostname for target IP address in /etc/hosts&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
